<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<package xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/packaging/2013/05/nuspec.xsd">
  <metadata>
    <id>CSharpGameLibrary</id>
    <version>0.1.5-alpha</version>
    <title>C# Game Library</title>
    <authors>Ryan Vazquez</authors>
    <owners>vazgriz</owners>
    <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
    <licenseUrl>https://github.com/vazgriz/CSharpGameLibrary/blob/master/license.txt</licenseUrl>
    <projectUrl>https://github.com/vazgriz/CSharpGameLibrary</projectUrl>
    <description>C# bindings for GLFW, OpenGL, and Vulkan</description>
    <releaseNotes>- Vulkan
  - Fix bug in Instance creation
  - Fix bugs in DebugReportCallback
  - Remove non default constructor from DeviceCreateInfo
  - Remove non default constructor from DeviceQueueCreateInfo
  - Remove non default constructor from SwapchainCreateInfo
  - Remove non default constructors from ShaderModuleCreateInfo
  - CommandBuffer
    - Implement IDisposable
    - Remove Draw overload
    - Remove BindDescriptorSets overloads
    - Remove CopyBuffer overload
    - Rename BindVertexBuffer to BindVertexBuffers
    - Add overloads to CopyBufferToImage, CopyImageToBuffer, BlitImage, ClearColorImage, SetViewports, SetScissor, ClearAttachments, and ResolveImage
  - CommandPool
    - Add Free overload
  - DescriptorSet
    - Add CopyDescriptorSet class
    - Add support for copying descriptors
    - Add Layouts property
  - DescriptorPool
    - Add MaxSets property
    - Add PoolSizes property
  - DescriptorSetLayout
    - Add Bindings property
  - Buffer
    - Size property now returns the value of the size field in the BufferCreateInfo
  - BufferView
    - Add Buffer property
    - Add Format property
  - Pipeline
    - Add Flags property
    - Add Layout property
    - ComputePipeline
      - Add BasePipeline property
    - GraphicsPipeline
      - Add BasePipeline property
  - Framebuffer
    - Add Attachments property
  - Image
    - Add SharingMode property
	- Add QueueFamilyIndices property
  - Exceptions
    - Add VulkanException class
    - Change all classes in CSGL.Vulkan to throw exceptions inheriting from VulkanException
    - Add QueryPoolException
    - Add CommandBufferException
  - Fix structs in CSGL.Vulkan
    - VkImageBlit
    - VkPhysicalDeviceLimits
  - Change enum value names for:
    - VkQueryResultFlags
    - VkSampleCountFlags
    - VkSurfaceTransformsFlagsKHR
    - VkBlendFactor
    - VkFormat
    - VkImageType
    - VkImageViewType
    - VkIndexType
- GLFW
  - Fix bug that caused managed delegate to be garbage collected
- Add Interop.AddressOf method
- Fix bug in Interop.GetInternalArray</releaseNotes>
